---
title: Saucy Beef & Sesame Rice Balls with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Get ready for a flavour-packed bite! These sesame rice balls are definitely the star of the show - crispy, golden, and downright addictive. Paired with a saucy chicken and veggie stir-fry, every mouthful is a perfect mix of crunch, umami, and freshness. Dinner just got a whole lot more fun!
